DATA: gv_a Value 'A',
      gv_b VALUE 'B',
      gv_c VALUE 'C',
      gv_d VALUE 'D'.

PERFORM test USING gv_a gv_b
             CHANGING gv_c gv_d.
New-line.

write: 'PERFORM End: ', gv_a, gv_b, gv_c, gv_d.
